OASISFormat: 0.4
Name:        OcLaunch
Version:     0.1.3
Synopsis:    Launch commands automatically
Authors:     Joly Clément <leowzukw@vmail.me>
Maintainers: Joly Clément <leowzukw@vmail.me>
License:     CeCILL
